{"tid":1245974,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[環保撚］半送舊教科書，有意自修/當私補教材嘅巴絲入黎睇睇","createTime":"2019-06-20T13:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T15:06:49.000Z","uid":162095,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cb3bf986f474d585d097c7509bb5517b22aa60a1","tid":1245974,"uid":162095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:45:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟都grad咗一段時間<br />\n但最近先立心清一清啲舊教科書<br />\n但扔晒佢又好可惜<br />\n就諗到不如送比有需要嘅人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果各位巴絲睇啱邊本又唔嫌殘舊就隨便講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於點解標題有個半字呢<br />\n如果住得近就冇嘢<br />\n但交收地點較遠的話就想收返20蚊車馬費<br />\n請原諒小弟住得偏少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoqNbfP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoqNbfP.png&h=ce567d3c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qoG8E9d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqoG8E9d.png&h=0e320194&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjkpXVX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjkpXVX.png&h=4f13210b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xsa5HnG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXsa5HnG.png&h=eb116888&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jjnzAHK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjjnzAHK.png&h=ff4ef357&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLU982M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLU982M.png&h=5f5cec9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講返先，個4本phy係練習黎<br />\n2本mc 2本structural question<br />\n2本細嘅就係learning handbook<br />\n<br />\n綠色個本m2 mock paper<br />\n用鉛筆做咗mock1幾版<br />\n其餘5份mock就完全新嘅<br />\n<br />\n有興趣請留tg講聲<br />\nBtw 21號嘅msg可能未咁快覆，大家知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不排除未來會更新，thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0228ca79b854eb30c0a7b9a459eedb837187706","tid":1245974,"uid":162095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:50:23.000Z","msg":"Phy練習都係全新<br />\n另外要嘅話盡量成set要，thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28dc596a5441bac4e65384ed456b3c06e286710","tid":1245974,"uid":162095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WNHf4OK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWNHf4OK.png&h=b744edda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nChem書，缺3、4"},{"pid":"d0b184b15e81d9682401a33f8cd270feeacbc497","tid":1245974,"uid":162095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:33:58.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f5ba1ad72ef2f1ce5de050b6246c38939a4f48","tid":1245974,"uid":162095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:04:29.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7a76a9fdc291111e5840a1b07ef7281234a719","tid":1245974,"uid":135827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde5b1936b556a7a276d22b13a2274545540bedf","tid":1245974,"uid":162095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b7a76a9fdc291111e5840a1b07ef7281234a719","tid":1245974,"uid":135827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda98c0e916ae98e0d581dddbba90b70e65c1be0","tid":1245974,"uid":162095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep